headline: AutoZone (AZO): 3 Reasons We Love This Stock
summary: AutoZone currently trades at $4,199 and has been a dream stock for shareholders. It’s returned 236% since September 2020, nearly tripling the S&P 500’s 80.3% gain. The company has also beaten the index over the past six months as its stock price is up 20.7%.
